# Optional environment for systemd (Debian/Ubuntu style).
#
# Copy to /etc/default/ip-signal-duplicator and uncomment or extend as needed.
# The unit file loads this with: EnvironmentFile=-/etc/default/ip-signal-duplicator
#
# PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 is already set in the unit; repeat here only if you override ExecStart.
# Add any extra Environment=KEY=value lines you need for a custom wrapper (not read by the stock script).
